 ### Changed
 
+* The default code style has been changed from `intellij_idea` to `ktlint_official`. The `ktlint_official` codestyle adheres to the best parts of the [Kotlin Coding Conventions](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/coding-conventions.html) and [Android Kotlin styleguide](https://developer.android.com/kotlin/style-guide).
